\u03c3</span><span class=\"mord sqrt\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\"><span class=\"svg-align\"><span class=\"pstrut\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathdefault\">t</span></span></span><span class=\"\"><span class=\"pstrut\"></span><span class=\"hide-tail\"></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">\u200b</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\"><span class=\"\"></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"\"><span class=\"pstrut\"></span><span class=\"frac-line\"></span></span><span class=\"\"><span class=\"pstrut\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathdefault\">l</span><span class=\"mord mathdefault\">n</span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"delimsizing size3\">(</span></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mopen nulldelimiter\"></span><span class=\"mfrac\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\"><span class=\"\"><span class=\"pstrut\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\"><span class=\"mord mathdefault mtight\">K</span></span></span></span><span class=\"\"><span class=\"pstrut\"></span><span class=\"frac-line\"></span></span><span class=\"\"><span class=\"pstrut\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\"><span class=\"mord mathdefault mtight\">S</span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">\u200b</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\"><span class=\"\"></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mclose nulldelimiter\"></span></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"delimsizing size3\">)</span></span><span class=\"mspace\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">+</span><span class=\"mspace\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"delimsizing size3\">(</span></span><span class=\"mord mathdefault\">r</span><span class=\"mspace\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">+</span><span class=\"mspace\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mopen nulldelimiter\"></span><span class=\"mfrac\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\"><span class=\"\"><span class=\"pstrut\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">2</span></span></span></span><span class=\"\"><span class=\"pstrut\"></span><span class=\"frac-line\"></span></span><span class=\"\"><span class=\"pstrut\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\"><span class=\"mord mathdefault mtight\">\u03c3</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\"><span class=\"\"><span class=\"pstrut\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size3 size1 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">2</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">\u200b</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\"><span class=\"\"></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mclose nulldelimiter\"></span></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"delimsizing size3\">)</span></span><span class=\"mord mathdefault\">t</span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">\u200b</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\"><span class=\"\"></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mclose nulldelimiter\"></span></span></span></span><span class=\"\"><span class=\"pstrut\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord\"></span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord textbf\">where:</span></span></span></span><span class=\"\"><span class=\"pstrut\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord\"></span><span class=\"mord mathdefault\">K</span><span class=\"mspace\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\"></span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord\">option\u00a0strike\u00a0price</span></span></span></span><span class=\"\"><span class=\"pstrut\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord\"></span><span class=\"mord mathdefault\">N</span><span class=\"mspace\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\"></span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord\">standard\u00a0normal\u00a0cumulative\u00a0distribution\u00a0function</span></span></span></span><span class=\"\"><span class=\"pstrut\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord\"></span><span class=\"mord mathdefault\">r</span><span class=\"mspace\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\"></span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord\">risk\u00a0free\u00a0interest\u00a0rate</span></span></span></span><span class=\"\"><span class=\"pstrut\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord\"></span><span class=\"mord mathdefault\">\u03c3</span><span class=\"mspace\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\"></span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord\">volatility\u00a0of\u00a0the\u00a0underlying</span></span></span></span><span class=\"\"><span class=\"pstrut\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord\"></span><span class=\"mord mathdefault\">S</span><span class=\"mspace\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\"></span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord\">price\u00a0of\u00a0the\u00a0underlying</span></span></span></span><span class=\"\"><span class=\"pstrut\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord\"></span><span class=\"mord mathdefault\">t</span><span class=\"mspace\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\"></span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord\">time\u00a0to\u00a0option\u2019s\u00a0expiry</span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">\u200b</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\"><span class=\"\"></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>\ufeff\ufeff\n", "\nVomma is a second-order Greek derivative which means that its value provides insight on how vega will change with the <a data-component=\"link\" data-ordinal=\"1\" data-source=\"inlineLink\" data-type=\"internalLink\" href=\"https://www.investopedia.com/terms/i/iv.asp\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">implied volatility</a> of the underlying instrument. If a positive vomma is calculated and volatility increases, vega on the option position will increase.\u00a0If volatility falls, a positive vomma would indicate a decrease in vega. If vomma is negative, the opposite occurs with volatility changes as indicated by vega\u2019s convexity.\n", "\nGenerally, investors with long options should look for a high, positive value for vomma, while investors with short options should look for a negative one.\n", "\nThe formula for calculating vomma\u00a0is below:\n", "\n<span data-value=\"\\begin{aligned} \\text{Vomma} = \\frac{ \\partial \\nu}{\\partial \\sigma} = \\frac{\\partial ^ 2V}{\\partial\\sigma ^ 2} \\end{aligned}\">\ufeff<span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\">\n<math>\n<semantics>\n<mtable>\n<mtr>\n<mtd>\n<mstyle>\n<mrow>\n<mtext>\nVomma\n</mtext>\n<mo>\n=\n</mo>\n<mfrac>\n<mrow>\n<mi>\n\u2202\n</mi>\n<mi>\n\u03bd\n</mi>\n</mrow>\n<mrow>\n<mi>\n\u2202\n</mi>\n<mi>\n\u03c3\n</mi>\n</mrow>\n</mfrac>\n<mo>\n=\n</mo>\n<mfrac>\n<mrow>\n<msup>\n<mi>\n\u2202\n</mi>\n<mn>\n2\n</mn>\n</msup>\n<mi>\nV\n</mi>\n</mrow>\n<mrow>\n<mi>\n\u2202\n</mi>\n<msup>\n<mi>\n\u03c3\n</mi>\n<mn>\n2\n</mn>\n</msup>\n</mrow>\n</mfrac>\n</mrow>\n</mstyle>\n</mtd>\n</mtr>\n</mtable>\n<annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\n\\begin{aligned} \\text{Vomma} = \\frac{ \\partial \\nu}{\\partial \\sigma} = \\frac{\\partial ^ 2V}{\\partial\\sigma ^ 2} \\end{aligned}\n</annotation>\n</semantics>\n</math></span><span class=\"katex-html\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mtable\"><span class=\"col-align-r\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\"><span class=\"\"><span 